# Scripts

- 02_Metrics_FTed_Model.ipynb
To compute the validation metrics.

- pre_augment_dataset.py
For data augmentation. The output will consist of two augmented versions for each 10-second clip, such as audio_1, audio_1_augmentedA, and audio_1_augmentedB.

- Run_FT.py
Tu run the fine-tuning.

- MFA.ipynb
To execute the MFA process. Generates 10-second clips of the original audio files. The final dataset underwent manual verification to ensure its accuracy.
